text: In this experiement there will be 4 blocks. Press "Next" to enter the block.

In this task, you will hear a sequence of syllables with different pitches, a pause, then a singular syllable. Your task is to determine whether this singular SYLLABLE is in the previous sequence. After hearing the singular syllable, you will be prompted to indicate whether the syllable was "absent" or "present" from the sequence. Press "Next" to start trials.
